@startuml Rental State Machine
skinparam nodesep 60

[*] --> Requested

Requested --> Approved : owner: approve
Requested --> Rejected : owner: reject
Requested --> Rejected : [auto] start date passed

Approved --> OutForRent : owner: confirm handover

OutForRent --> Returned : borrower: mark returned
OutForRent --> Overdue : [auto] end date passed

Overdue --> Returned : borrower: mark returned

Returned --> Completed : owner: confirm receipt

Rejected --> [*]
Completed --> [*]

state Overdue : Set automatically on read\nwhen EndDate < today
state Rejected : Terminal state
state Completed : Terminal state\nReview may be submitted
@enduml
